description:
Ulrich Kesler was an admiral of the http://anidb.net/ch1534 [Galactic Empire] who served as the Superintendent of the Imperial http://anidb.net/ch6228 [Military Police]. Among http://anidb.net/ch186 [Reinhard von Lohengramm]`s original admirals, Kesler commanded a fleet the least amount of times. His accolades are better represented by his police work and reforms of the Imperial justice system.
Source: Gineipaedia
name: Ulrich Kesler
